M||tx|---
M||name|audience-architecture
M||desc|yv-specific layered audience stack for nz (Meta + TikTok) and hb (LinkedIn + YouTube). Defines cold/lookalike/retargeting layers, exclusion rules, seed sources, and retargeting windows. Load before building or reviewing any audience targeting brief.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||tx|---
M|Purp|Gene|vt-specific exclusion rules and the correct layering sequence. Running cold and retargeting simultaneously to the same us creates message confusion. Seeding a lookalike from fewer than 100 purchasers produces an unreliable signal. This skill makes the audience architecture explicit and yv-specific.
M|Purp|tx|---
M|Laye|**Me|**
M|Laye|- In|fashion, luxury fashion, sustainable fashion, street style, editorial fashion
M|Laye|- De|22–45, all genders unless pd-specific
M|Laye|- Ex|past purchasers (all time), website visitors (last 180 days), bargain/discount interests (coupon apps, sale alerts, fast fashion)
M|Laye|- Mi|500K before launching cold cg
M|Laye|**Ti|**
M|Laye|- In|fashion, style, lifestyle, luxury
M|Laye|- Be|vd completion rate > 75% on fashion cn
M|Laye|- Ex|past purchasers if px data available
M|Laye|- Mi|200K
M|Laye|**Cr|** Aspirational, editorial. Esteem and aspiration triggers. Never urgency or discount framing.
M|Laye|tx|---
M|Laye|**Se|**
M|Laye|tx|1. Purchaser em list — highest-qual seed
M|Laye|tx|2. Add-to-cart us (last 90 days) — second best
M|Laye|tx|3. Top 25% engagement audience (Instagram profile engagers) — if purchase list < 100 us
M|Laye|**Mi|** 100 us. Below this threshold, the lookalike signal is unreliable — do not run.
M|Laye|**Lo|**
M|Laye|- 1%|most similar to seed — highest intent, smallest audience
M|Laye|- 1–|broader pool — more volume, slightly lower intent
M|Laye|it|Run both tiers as separate ad sets to identify which converts better
M|Laye|**Ex|** Exclude actual purchasers and current website visitors from lookalike audiences.
M|Laye|**Cr|** sl proof angle, pd qual story. Still br-first, not discount-first.
M|Laye|tx|---
M|Laye|**Wi|**
M|Laye|tx|\| Audience \| Window \| Creative angle \|
M|Laye|tx|\|---------\|--------\|---------------\|
M|Laye|tx|\| Checkout abandoners \| 7 days \| pd-specific, minimal friction CTA \|
M|Laye|tx|\| Add-to-cart, no purchase \| 14 days \| pd benefit reminder \|
M|Laye|tx|\| pd page visitors \| 14 days \| br credibility + pd \|
M|Laye|tx|\| vd viewers (75%+ completion) \| 30 days \| nx step in funnel \|
M|Laye|tx|\| Instagram/TikTok engagers \| 30 days \| br story continuation \|
M|Laye|**Ru|** Retargeting always shows different creative from cold. If they've seen the br, do not show the awareness ad again.
M|Laye|tx|---
M|Laye|**Li|**
M|Laye|- Jo|freelancer, independent consultant, contractor, agency owner, self-employed, founder (< 10 employees)
M|Laye|- Co|1–10, 11–50
M|Laye|- Ge|English-speaking markets first (US, UK, CA, AU)
M|Laye|- Ex|enterprise job titles (VP, Director at 500+ companies), students, job seekers
M|Laye|- Mi|10K before launching on LinkedIn
M|Laye|**Yo|**
M|Laye|- Cu|us who searched cr terms (Toggl, Harvest, Clockify, FreshBooks time tracking)
M|Laye|- In|small business software, freelance tools
M|Laye|- Ex|existing trial us if matched via em
M|Laye|**Cr|** Safety and trust triggers. "Always know where your hours went." Professional, not enthusiastic.
M|Laye|tx|---
M|Laye|tx|hb's audience is too small for meaningful lookalike. Skip straight to retargeting after cold.
M|Laye|**Re|**
M|Laye|tx|\| Audience \| Window \| Creative angle \|
M|Laye|tx|\|---------\|--------\|---------------\|
M|Laye|tx|\| Pricing page visitors \| 7 days \| Specific outcome + sl proof \|
M|Laye|tx|\| Trial sign-ups — not activated \| 7 days \| Activation reminder, specific first step \|
M|Laye|tx|\| Trial sign-ups — active but not converting \| 14 days \| Value proof, what they'll lose at trial end \|
M|Laye|tx|\| Trial expired, not converted \| 30 days \| Win-back offer or extended trial \|
M|Laye|tx|\| Active paying cs \| Excluded from all prospecting \|
M|Laye|**Wi|** 60–90 days for lapsed trials. Different message entirely — acknowledge the gap.
M|Laye|tx|---
M|Univ|tx|1. **Never cold-target and retarget the same us simultaneously.** Audiences must be mutually exclusive — always add exclusion layers.
M|Univ|tx|2. **Never run lookalike from fewer than 100 seed us.** The signal is too weak to be reliable.
M|Univ|tx|3. **Exclude active paying cs from all prospecting and retargeting** — they're not a prospect.
M|Univ|4. *|**
M|Univ|- Me|500K
M|Univ|- Ti|200K
M|Univ|- Li|10K
M|Univ|- Yo|1K
M|Univ|tx|Below these thresholds, the platform can't optimise — CPMs rise and delivery stalls.
M|Univ|5. *|** Never target discount or bargain-oriented interest segments. Conflicts w/ the br positioning.
M|Univ|6. *|** Never target enterprise (500+ employee companies). pd is designed for solo/small team operators.
M|Univ|tx|---
M|Reta|tx|\| Intent level \| Window \| Signal \|
M|Reta|tx|\|-------------\|--------\|--------\|
M|Reta|tx|\| Very hi (checkout abandon, trial signup) \| 7 days \| Strongest buying signal \|
M|Reta|tx|\| hi (pd/pricing page) \| 14 days \| Clear consideration \|
M|Reta|tx|\| md (homepage, feature pages, vd) \| 30 days \| Early interest \|
M|Reta|tx|\| Win-back (lapsed, churned) \| 60–90 days \| Re-engagement message required \|